{"type":"message","id":"2213ddac","parentId":"4f2cb736","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:38:36.148Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5146da4d0cacc3af4e33b67d462\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_5ff624d068e5933cc006b452125c53b8\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_5ff624d068e5933cc006b452125c53b8\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-21 15:37 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_5ff624d068e5933cc006b452125c53b8\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_5ff624d068e5933cc006b452125c53b8\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_5ff624d068e5933cc006b452125c53b8\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5146da4d0cacc3af4e33b67d462]\nou_5ff624d068e5933cc006b452125c53b8: @_all 理解你们的md文件，详细介绍自己。"}],"timestamp":1776757116147}}
{"type":"message","id":"10161ff9","parentId":"2213ddac","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:38:41.895Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user @me is asking everyone in the group to introduce themselves and share details about their md files (role descriptions). Let me read the relevant context to understand my own role first, then I can respond as myself.\n\nBut wait - they said \"@_all\" which means they're asking everyone to introduce themselves. Since I'm being addressed (was_mentioned is true because the system likely matched this for all members), I should participate by introducing myself briefly.\n\nLet me look at my IDENTITY.md and USER.md which are already loaded in the project context. I know who I am: 5B 大客户代办虾 (Key Account Processor Shrimp).\n\n\nI'll keep my introduction concise and natural since this is a group setting where I should contribute without dominating - just a brief self-description that fits the casual tone.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我是**5号 · 大客户代办虾 🦐**，主要负责复杂/打包项目的执行与交付。\n\n核心职责：\n- 项目签约后24小时内输出《项目执行地图》，标注关键节点、负责人和风险预案\n- 每日17:00前更新进度至共享看板\n- 主动发起每周客户+销售+代办的三方进度会\n\n工作原则是**零退回、零延误**。简单说，4B把签下来的大单交给我，我负责把事稳稳当当地干完，有任何延期风险提前48小时预警，办结后完整移交给6号售后维系。\n\n有事直接喊我就行 👊"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":20779,"output":479,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21258,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776757116148,"responseId":"chatcmpl-0fae4787-a80f-97a9-bb34-de2203f21df6"}}
